    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are playing as cybernetically enhanced, armed-to-the-teeth animals inside a top-down, bullet-hell world trying to save your soul.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bullet-Hell Bosses!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Void Strife, there are varied bosses which can mess up your run in a lot of ways. The Brainiac, the biggest and baddest of all may have some surprises up its... membrane?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355070/extras/497e56874e65a58bda48cab86cda2aae.poster.avif?t=1746358087\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355070/extras/497e56874e65a58bda48cab86cda2aae.webm?t=1746358087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355070/extras/497e56874e65a58bda48cab86cda2aae.mp4?t=1746358087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Different animals to play as!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock a continuously updated cast of animals:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PUNKHORSE</strong>: More <strong>health</strong>. More <strong>mass</strong>. The most <strong>durable</strong> of all.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ARM4DILLO</strong>: <strong>FAST AS HECK</strong>. More damage the faster you go. <strong>Glass Cannon</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FISH-X</strong>: Small and manoeuvrable. Specialist in <strong>EXPLOSIONS</strong>.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tons of unique items!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Items  have the potential to change how your run is played entirely </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Magnum Opus</strong>: Lightning ball launcher. Lightning tendrils. See for yourself...</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Neutron Expansion</strong>: chance to explode on <strong>every</strong> attack. Hook that bad boy up with <strong>FISH-X</strong> and BOOM. You just cleared the whole screen.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355070/extras/7d8fe6abf8ad71e49eea762d3f4295ee.poster.avif?t=1746358087\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355070/extras/7d8fe6abf8ad71e49eea762d3f4295ee.webm?t=1746358087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355070/extras/7d8fe6abf8ad71e49eea762d3f4295ee.mp4?t=1746358087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Void Strife, you can also recombobulate items: this combines all of their powers and effects into one item. With this alone you can become a busted-ahh horse. Or fish. LOOK HOW MANY BULLETS!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355070/extras/5fe87f9136979956a09ad64fb13e10d1.poster.avif?t=1746358087\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355070/extras/5fe87f9136979956a09ad64fb13e10d1.webm?t=1746358087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355070/extras/5fe87f9136979956a09ad64fb13e10d1.mp4?t=1746358087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
